Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.05,0:00:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.02,0:00:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.13,0:00:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.04,0:00:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.14,0:00:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.15,0:00:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.89,0:00:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.86,0:00:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.17,0:01:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.14,0:01:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.63,0:01:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天,三鷹沒來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.97,0:01:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.13,0:02:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請起來啊,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.10,0:02:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是答覆我求婚的重要日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然如此草率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.58,0:02:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.16,0:02:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#59 心跳不已!\N九條明日菜的初體驗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.47,0:02:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.41,0:02:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,是一之瀨太太啊,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.28,0:02:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,你是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.62,0:03:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐的情況怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如說,有沒有在生氣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.39,0:03:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道,你等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還在氣我\N那天早上才回來的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.42,0:03:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,怎麼了?一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的好像在生氣耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.39,0:03:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.39,0:03:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我覺得你不需要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可以不在意\N這一切都是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.90,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.03,0:03:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天,我跟她約好要見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為突然生病,無法去赴約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.41,0:03:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我叫管理員來聽\N你直接跟她說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.41,0:04:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N我只是想知道她的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我改天再打電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.19,0:04:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?三鷹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說要叫妳來接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就急急忙忙把電話給掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.63,0:04:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼看來果然是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,快點起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開水快滿出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟三鷹教練之間\N發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.08,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的日子那天,我居然睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.25,0:04:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的日子?\N難不成是回覆求婚的日子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹向響子求婚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是正式的求婚喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果管理員怎麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她沒有否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.07,0:04:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能答應了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.10,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一來,五代還是\N瀟灑的退出才是上策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.27,0:05:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,被甩了還糾纏不清的傢伙\N會讓人很痛恨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.28,0:05:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說,前幾天管理員還做大餐\N等五代回來,不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有葡萄酒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.59,0:05:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,那八成是想找五代商量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是五代居然早上才回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來一切已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代本來就沒什麼勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.44,0:05:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還不老實說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.57,0:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經說過好幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想跟明日菜結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把理由說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.58,0:05:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟那個人進展到什麼地步?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經約好要結婚了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.09,0:05:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,因為有很多原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.36,0:06:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看是你自己一廂情願吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.87,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的好像在生氣耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿瞬\N你到底不喜歡明日菜哪一點?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.98,0:06:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼好的千金小姐\N現在打著燈籠都找不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.15,0:06:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天一定要給我一個\N能接受的理由,否則我就不走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.62,0:06:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是不通情理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.90,0:06:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也說說話啊,阿瞬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.43,0:06:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦\N事到如今也沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就老實說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.07,0:06:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔,你要答應我\N絕對不能說出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.04,0:06:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然這麼嚴肅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…我討厭小…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.89,0:07:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?我聽不見\N你說你討厭什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.80,0:07:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狗!我討厭小狗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恨死小狗了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.34,0:07:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭小狗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.27,0:07:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,所以我跟明日菜合不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.95,0:07:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你要說什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.55,0:07:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這種藉口行得通嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.02,0:07:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次準備個像樣一點的謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.62,0:07:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是謊言,我是真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.13,0:07:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我聽清楚!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.09,0:07:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和九条家的資產合併的話\N我們三鷹家就穩如泰山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.67,0:07:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不就變成策略聯姻了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.34,0:07:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在公寓講的話,有房客在不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.98,0:07:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她叫出來的話\N又怕她不肯出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.32,0:08:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫信…太灰暗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.62,0:08:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埋伏等她\N這樣搞不好會讓她更反感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.69,0:08:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有什麼好辦法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.43,0:08:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她正式回覆三鷹之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.53,0:08:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要把我的心意告訴她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.37,0:08:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為從那天之後\N她就一直不肯跟我說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.18,0:08:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日子,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.68,0:08:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要給我答覆喔,勾勾手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勾勾手一言為定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.09,0:08:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今今最喜歡五代哥哥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.99,0:08:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長大以後,要娶我當新娘喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是錄音帶情書嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代真是萬人迷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.03,0:08:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當小孩真好啊,好惡都很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.60,0:08:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,還有,我很會做菜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你的答覆喔,今今上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.39,0:09:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次真不好意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的很抱歉\N-真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.74,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.61,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.95,0:09:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,找到了找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.25,0:09:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿瞬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔,你怎麼跑來這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和明日菜約會的日子\N已經敲定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.05,0:09:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想快點通知你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.49,0:09:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼擅自做決定\N這樣我很困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今,有什麼好害羞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你們遲早都要結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.10,0:09:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小倆口見個面\N好好談談未來的規劃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有這個意思!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.34,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.91,0:10:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿瞬,離去的人不要追\N前來的人不要拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.80,0:10:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然婚事談得很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.53,0:10:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就老實跟我說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,總覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.98,0:10:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又好像有點落寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種心情真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,這麼快就回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.79,0:10:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟三鷹教練好好談過了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.13,0:11:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.27,0:11:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她開口跟我說話了耶\N這是個大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.74,0:11:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我深深的反省了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反省什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.51,0:11:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那天玩到早上才回來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事不要再談了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.85,0:11:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經是結束的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.19,0:11:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結…結束的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.13,0:11:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.63,0:11:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糾纏不清,只會更討人厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人活著要懂得放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.50,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,一群幸災樂禍的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要給我答覆喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.62,0:11:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟小孩子的約定一定要履行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子是很敏感的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒有那個心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以用這招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,開始錄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.97,0:12:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,請妳聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點太灰暗了\N又不是在做人生諮詢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.68,0:12:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,開朗一點,開朗一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始打工之後\N沒能好好照顧妳的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好像很蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.66,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,我絕對沒有忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,不只這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經開始存錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該知道是什麼資金吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存錢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.67,0:13:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改天要借我錢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要借我錢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.52,0:13:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.39,0:13:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確,我是個\N三流大學的貧窮學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然明年就要畢業就職了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.20,0:13:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,可能進不了一流公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.40,0:13:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣前途一片黑暗的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.90,0:13:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在無法現在立刻向妳求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.50,0:13:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺變得悲慘起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.17,0:14:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向貧窮低頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱…朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來對唱吧,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開卡拉0K大會啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.85,0:14:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.42,0:14:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治療失戀之痛\N喝酒唱歌最好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.59,0:14:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰失戀啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.36,0:14:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被甩男人的悲鳴聲\N今夜也迴響在夜空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.03,0:14:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男女之間的不可思議\N今夜明日都令人落淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.70,0:14:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,真難看啊,真丟臉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.31,0:14:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一號,由六本木朱美演唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.55,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.35,0:15:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼來了,一大清早的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.32,0:15:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何都想見妳一面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.42,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話,到裡面坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,這裡就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.37,0:15:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下我得去相親對象的家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.80,0:15:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔,你好像跟她有約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是要去正式拒絕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.17,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要\N清楚地做個了斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.11,0:15:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣妳願意把上次的答覆\N告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.08,0:15:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次的答覆?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是求婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,妳聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.06,0:16:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了妳去拒絕這樁婚事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下敲定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.54,0:16:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是刻意的演技\N能演到這種程度也很了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.54,0:16:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員好像很感動耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.67,0:16:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,請妳聽到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.68,0:16:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳當真想結婚\N我也不能阻止妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.58,0:16:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,在妳做決定之前\N希望妳能聽我說幾句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.35,0:17:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳,或是我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.09,0:17:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些話實在無法表達\N我的真正心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是每次妳對我展露笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.93,0:17:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就有一種無法言喻的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.34,0:17:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.27,0:17:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所感覺到的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也希望也能讓妳感受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.45,0:17:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力成為這樣的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.22,0:17:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜,三鷹先生來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.83,0:17:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她為了和你約會\N還特別打扮了一下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.30,0:17:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜,三鷹先生在等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.43,0:17:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.27,0:17:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,為了給大家打扮\N花了一點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給小狗們打扮?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.11,0:17:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該不會是要帶小狗去吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.59,0:18:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不行\N都這個年紀了,妳在想什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-對不對?\N-對對對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.03,0:18:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你的臉色不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.53,0:18:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我帶令千金出去玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.90,0:18:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了這個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子們好像真的很想跟來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜,我要加速囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.87,0:18:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了妳去拒絕這樁婚事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是我的真正心聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.34,0:19:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很期待今天的約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.54,0:19:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是你第一次約我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.35,0:19:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那麼開心,我就更傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然挺可憐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳冷靜地聽我說幾句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.84,0:20:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳那麼年輕美麗\N無論家世背景或學歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.28,0:20:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我在一起真是太委屈妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.94,0:20:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,不來了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.91,0:20:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣誇讚人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.18,0:20:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,請妳聽到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.42,0:20:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像妳這麼優秀的女孩\N與其跟我在一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.53,0:20:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.50,0:20:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到你的時候\N我就在心裡決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個,妳先聽我說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是那些孩子們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.31,0:20:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.69,0:20:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那些孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.03,0:21:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大老遠的追到這裡來\N讓人既感動又心疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.23,0:21:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡,大家快過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.21,0:21:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們換個地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.71,0:21:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那些孩子們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.59,0:21:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有生以來第一次\N被男人抱在懷裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.60,0:21:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟著他一輩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.78,0:21:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是叫我聽裡面的錄音帶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.50,0:22:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今今,妳好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.87,0:22:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是五代哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.77,0:22:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要當我的新娘?\N這是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.64,0:22:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡今今喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.18,0:22:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以真的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.58,0:22:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在房間裡開心得大叫萬歲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.72,0:22:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她明白我的心意了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.86,0:22:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.33,0:22:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,今今妳還很小\N不能娶妳當新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.10,0:22:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.57,0:22:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.74,0:22:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是\N不娶妳當老婆,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.41,0:22:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是無話可說,害我都想放屁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.72,0:23:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代說這是他的真正心聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.76,0:23:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子\N(響子和今日子同音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.46,0:23:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說,我現在還沒有信心\N能夠讓妳得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.23,0:23:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.27,0:23:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.50,0:23:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日子幼稚園的褓父\N給今日子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.54,0:23:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.18,0:23:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,我愛妳的心情\N不輸給任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.52,0:23:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,我要跟大哥哥結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.28,0:23:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔,好棒喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.93,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!管理員和三鷹\N演出親熱場面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.64,0:23:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,聽說在三鷹的公寓抱在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.40,0:23:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代的打擊應該會很大吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.61,0:23:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.24,0:23:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『看見了!\N響子和三鷹突然上了二壘?』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.24,0:24:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,我…
